                                Dear <span style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">Roshan Mehta</span>,
                                <br/><br/>
                                I trust this message finds you well.
                                <br/><br/>
                                We are pleased to announce the addition of a new team member,
                                <span style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">
                                    <t t-out="object.partner_name or ''"/>
                                </span>,
                                who will be joining our
                                <span style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">
                                    <t t-out="object.department_id.name or ''"/>
                                </span>.
