                                <br/><br/>
                                We appreciate your prompt attention to this matter to ensure a seamless onboarding experience.<br/>
                                If you have any questions or need further information, feel free to reach out to
                                <span style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: bold;">
                                    <div class="d-flex align-items-center mb-1"><a t-att-href="'mailto:'+user.login" t-esc="user.login"/></div>
                                </span>
                                <br/><br/>
                                Thank you for your cooperation.
                                <br/><br/>
                                Best regards,
                                <br/><br/>
                                <h5 class="mb-1"><b t-esc="user.signature"/></h5>
                            </div>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                </table>
            </field>
            <field name="auto_delete" eval="False"/>
        </record>

